{"tid":96249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反侵活動爆衝突 《變形金剛》男主角被捕","createTime":"2017-01-26T16:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T16:09:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bafdab968f73bfb0d3564144998954a711a7b82","tid":96249,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170126/large/1485420918_08c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2Flarge%2F1485420918_08c0.jpg&h=3b93c3c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國男星沙拉保夫（Shia LaBeouf）為反對美國總統特朗普正式上任，喺紐約嘅美國移動影像博物館門外發起咗一項4年持續抗議運動，佢帶領群眾對住鏡頭不停講「佢唔會分化我哋」，而呢個鏡頭會喺特朗普嘅4年任期內一直擺放，24小時不停錄影。 <br />\n<br />\n連日嚟都有唔少人參與，亦有滋事分子嚟搞事，於當地時間周三晚，沙拉保夫因與人發生衝突被捕。據紐約警方透露，當時一名男子對着鏡頭，講咗一啲關於特朗普嘅嘢，引起沙拉保夫不滿，而喺衝突過程中，沙拉保夫拉住方圍巾，又抓傷對方塊面。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，沙拉保夫向來火爆又神化已經唔係首次被捕。沙拉保夫曾於2005年認為鄰居擋住去路，失控駕車撞向對方座駕，之後持刀威脅鄰居，又曾試過喺2008年疑因醉駕發生車禍，而喺2011年，佢就因為喺酒吧與人衝突被捕。"},{"pid":"6bc1f7c18d7314284d481878f30a1874604f0ebc","tid":96249,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"Just do it!"},{"pid":"8995f05d1cf62b1755548646c3acb583905e4910","tid":96249,"uid":76930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"Just do it"},{"pid":"7af2519ff1266a7e5ee5ae0fddd673ab3633176f","tid":96249,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"又係Shia Lebeouf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0u4M6vppCI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do0u4M6vppCI&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=656edcb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0u4M6vppCI</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n